Excellent location!

9.8

Situated in Boston and with Back Bay Station reachable within 700 metres, The Lenox features concierge services, non-smoking rooms, a restaurant, free WiFi throughout the property and a bar. This 4-star hotel offers room service and an ATM. Private parking is available on site. Round-the-clock assistance is available at the reception, where staff speak Arabic, Greek, English and Spanish. Popular points of interest near the hotel include Hynes Convention Center, Boston Public Garden and Boston Museum of Fine Arts. The nearest airport is Logan Airport, 9 km from The Lenox.

Couples particularly like the location — they rated it 9.8 for a two-person trip.
